item.title: Guest Episode with Haunting Angels
item.description: On this special guest episode of Hidden In The Shadows, Isaac is joined by the North Carolina-based team, Haunting Angels. In this episode, Isaac delves deep with Sierra and Yvette from the team, exploring their most chilling paranormal experiences, the origins of Haunting Angels, and their vision for the future of paranormal investigation. Sierra and Yvette share their spookiest encounters, recounting tales from both local haunts and distant locations... Feed: https://feeds.acast.com/public/shows/6275e5d406c2840012321df2
